{"build_type":"executable","description":"Text search across package sources (what grep is NOT — grep matches instruction KINDS only). Request (argv[1]): {\"grep-text\": {\"roots\": [\"<dir>\",...], \"query\": \"<text>\"}}. Enumerates every package under roots and reports the path of each whose RAW .ipm source contains the query substring (function names, field values, any literal text). Emits {matches:[path,...], match_count, packages_scanned} on stdout. Bad request (no argv, unparseable, no arg object, no roots, no query) -> clean JSON {error}. Reuses parse_argument_vector_json_request, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, add_str_field, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output, enumerate_universe_packages, begin_empty_sequence_document_value, grep_text_scan, count_members_inside_container_value, begin_empty_mapping_document_value, attach_named_member_inside_mapping, add_number_to_object.","module_name":"search-textual-content-across-package-sources","package_name":"search-textual-content-across-package-sources","function_definitions":{"search-textual-content-across-package-sources":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_roots","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"roots"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_files","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"files"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_query","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"query"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_matches","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":